    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process of designing visual communications and text for commercial applications, usually to be printed or reproduced photographically, such as in advertisements, books, magazines, newspapers, leaflets, posters, diagrams, trademarks, corporate identities, sign systems, packaging, film, television graphics, etc.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
